subject: Olympic Games (2008)
Volleyball
Traffic Accidents and Safety
lead_paragraph: Stacy Sykora, a member of the United States’ silver-medal team at the 2008 Beijing Olympics sustained a head injury after the bus she was riding on crashed on its way to a match.
